libevent::event_assign(
&raw_event_, base, fd_,
EV_PERSIST | (trigger_ == FileTriggerType::Edge ? EV_ET : 0) |
(events & FileReadyType::Read ? EV_READ : 0) |
(events & FileReadyType::Write ? EV_WRITE : 0) |
(events & FileReadyType::Closed ? EV_CLOSED : 0),
callback,
(FileEventImpl)this
)
